high_descs: Turn right and walk to the kettle on the counter to the right of the oven.
Pick up the kettle from the counter.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the kettle in the sink, turn the water on, then turn it off and pick the kettle up.
Turn left and walk to the side of the black table closer to the refrigerator.
Put the kettle on the table to the left of the plant and next to the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Wash the kettle in the sink and put in on the black table.

high_descs: turn right and walk to the beginning of the rug underneath your feet, then turn left to walk over to the kitchen counter
grab the tea kettle off of the kitchen counter there
move to the right a bit so you can face the kitchen sink to your left
place the tea kettle inside of the right side kitchen sink, and fill it up with water, then pick it back up
turn left and walk over to the round kitchen table at the end of the room on your left
place the tea kettle down on the table behind the tomato and to the left of the plant
anns.task_desc: place a tea kettle with water inside on the kitchen table

high_descs: Walk to the right, turn left near the window, walk straight to the counter top between the stove and the sink.
Pick up the tea pot on top of the counter top.
Walk to the right a little bit to go to the sink.
Put the tea pot in the sink, turn on the water for a while, turn it off, and pick up the tea pot again.
Walk to the left, turn to the left near the fridge and go to the black round table.
Put the tea pot on the table and to the left of the plant.
anns.task_desc: Put the tea pot on the black round table to the left of the plant.
